object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct transactioninfo.SystemId, transactioninfo.ParentId, transactioninfo.CMMContainer, transactioninfo.Id, transactioninfo.TransactionCd, transactioninfo.TransactionEffectiveDt, transactioninfo.TransactionEffectiveTm, transactioninfo.TransactionUser, transactioninfo.TransactionDt, transactioninfo.TransactionTm, transactioninfo.TransactionShortDescription, transactioninfo.TransactionLongDescription, transactioninfo.ChangeInfoRef, transactioninfo.TransactionNumber, transactioninfo.SubmissionNumber, transactioninfo.InforceChangePremiumAmt, transactioninfo.InforcePremiumAmt, transactioninfo.WrittenPremiumAmt, transactioninfo.CancelTypeCd, transactioninfo.CancelRequestedByCd, transactioninfo.PremiumCalculationDt, transactioninfo.RewriteToProductVersion, transactioninfo.NewPolicyEffectiveDt, transactioninfo.NewPolicyExpirationDt, transactioninfo.ReleaseHoldReason, transactioninfo.BookDt, transactioninfo.MasterTransactionNumber, transactioninfo.ReplacementOfTransactionNumber, transactioninfo.UnApplyOfTransactionNumber, transactioninfo.StatProcessedInd, transactioninfo.OutputTypeCd, transactioninfo.HoldType, transactioninfo.SourceCd, transactioninfo.DelayInvoiceInd, transactioninfo.CheckNumber, transactioninfo.PaymentTypeCd, transactioninfo.PaymentAmt, transactioninfo.ConversionTemplateIdRef, transactioninfo.ConversionGroup, transactioninfo.ConversionJobRef, transactioninfo.RenewalProviderRef, transactioninfo.RenewalSubProducerCd, transactioninfo.CommissionChangeInd, transactioninfo.PrevStatusCd, transactioninfo.FutureTermAutoTransactionInd, transactioninfo.UnapplySource, transactioninfo.ChargeReinstatementFeeInd, transactioninfo.OverrideInd, transactioninfo.SignatureDocument, transactioninfo.RowId 
FROM
 transactioninfo  transactioninfo   inner join advrxxchangedbeans advrxxchangedbeans
on  transactioninfo.Systemid=advrxxchangedbeans.Systemid
and  transactioninfo.cmmcontainer=advrxxchangedbeans.cmmcontainer
where  transactioninfo.CmmContainer='Application'
and concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt'
